name: I'm Victoria
intro: I'm a front-end developer with passion in creating user freindly SPAs, making illustrations and playing video games and DnD.
abouttxt: My name is Victoria Rogatinskaya, a Front End developer. I love making websites, art and playing too much DnD. I have experience building adaptive websites in VueJS and a special interest in usability and web performance.
